		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_FIRST_MEET_LEADER_MAYA_gkls621_ANY" Language="zh_Hant_HK">
			<Text>正讀倒讀都是大和麻彌。我是大和麻彌。請多關照~</Text>
